import f0 from './images/fruits/tile000.png'
import f1 from './images/fruits/tile001.png'
import f2 from './images/fruits/tile002.png'
import f3 from './images/fruits/tile003.png'
import f4 from './images/fruits/tile004.png'
import f5 from './images/fruits/tile005.png'
import f6 from './images/fruits/tile006.png'

const fruit = [
    {id: 0, img: f0, alt: 'tile000'},
    {id: 1, img: f1, alt: 'tile001'},
    {id: 2, img: f2, alt: 'tile002'},
    {id: 3, img: f3, alt: 'tile003'},
    {id: 4, img: f4, alt: 'tile004'},
    {id: 5, img: f5, alt: 'tile005'},
    {id: 6, img: f6, alt: 'tile006'},
]

function imageLoader()
{
    return fruit;
}

export default imageLoader;
